===========================
 PyBlosxom Release Process
===========================

1. Update the release process

2. Update CHANGELOG with bugs fixed for this version from Roundup.

3. Move old WHATSNEW content to docs/.

4. Update WHATSNEW

5. Update the version number and date in:

   * setup.py
   * Pyblosxom/pyblosxom.py
   * docs/conf.py

6. Update AUTHORS::

      git log --pretty=format:%an | sort -u

7. Commit the changes

8. Tag the commit::

      git tag -a pyblosxom_x_y

9. Build the tarball::

      git archive \
          --format=tar \
          --prefix=pyblosxom-x.y/ $TAG > pyblosxom-x.y.tar

   This builds the tarball.

10. Build the docs::

       cd docs/
       make html

11. Push the docs and the new tarball to the website.

12. Update PYPI::

       python setup.py register
